'''酈安治'''（'''Andrew Lih'''，{{bd|1968年|||}}）是[[华裔美国人|华裔美国人]]，[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]的[[客座教授|客座教授]]，<ref>[http://annenberg.usc.edu/Faculty/Communication%20and%20Journalism/LihA.aspx "Faculty: Andrew Lih"] {{Wayback|url=http://annenberg.usc.edu/Faculty/Communication%20and%20Journalism/LihA.aspx |date=20130507122710 }} at [[University_of_Southern_California|USC]] {{tsl|en|University of Southern California Annenberg School for Communication||Annenberg School for Communications and Journalism}}</ref><ref>Cohen, Noam. "[http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/16/technology/16wikipedia.html Chinese Government Relaxes Its Total Ban on Wikipedia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/16/technology/16wikipedia.html |date=20210113100820 }}." 《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》. 2006年10月16日. Retrieved on 2012年2月28日.</ref>[[维基百科|维基百科]]、[[中华人民共和国网络审查|中华人民共和国网络审查]]分析者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=92489122|title=How Do Chinese Citizens Feel About Censorship?|publisher=[[National_Public_Radio|National Public Radio]]|accessdate=May 11, 2009|last=Sydell|first=Laura|date=July 12, 2008|archive-date=2018-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628124737/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=92489122|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>
